        "<p>â€œNow you all know that people who do nothing worth while in this world</p>\n<p>are of no use and there is little room for them.</p>\n<p>So when Mother Nature</p>\n<p>saw how useless had become the Frog tribe she called the King Frog</p>\n<p>before her and she said:</p>\n<p>â€œ'Because you can think of nothing but your beautiful tail it shall be</p>\n<p>taken away from you.</p>\n",
