        "<h3>CHAPTER IV WHY JIMMY SKUNK WEARS STRIPES</h3>\n<p>Jimmy Skunk, as everybody knows, wears a striped suit, a suit of black</p>\n<p>and white.</p>\n<p>There was a time, long, long ago, when all the Skunk family</p>\n<p>wore black.</p>\n<p>Very handsome their coats were, too, a beautiful, glossy</p>\n<p>black.</p>\n",
